Adaar Tower - Hall of Dawn~
Warm golden light spills through tall crystal windows and dances across
white-stone floors veined with silver. Banners of the allied good races
hang from the high vaults, and the scent of cedar and incense steadies
new adventurers as they take their first steps into the wider world.
